
 To build :
   cd ./inexlib/exlib/examples/cpp
   ./build rshp.cpp
   ./build gui_shp_X11.cpp
 On a Mac:   
   ./build gui_shp_Cocoa.mm

 To have a light traceback, use the option -v as in:
   ./build -v <app>.cpp

 To run :
   ./bin_[gnu,clang]/rshp
   ./bin_[gnu,clang]/gui_shp_X11
 On a Mac:   
   open ./bin_clang/gui_shp_Cocoa.app
